01:20:51,170 --> 01:20:52,710
What will it be this time?

785
01:21:22,320 --> 01:21:24,490
Do you have a room available?

786
01:21:36,090 --> 01:21:38,500
Would you like two rooms?

787
01:21:39,000 --> 01:21:42,800
Just one, the cheapest.

788
01:21:47,100 --> 01:21:48,720
Thank you.

789
01:21:54,190 --> 01:21:57,150
Welcome, this way please.

790
01:21:58,520 --> 01:21:59,730
Please, as you are.

791
01:22:23,130 --> 01:22:25,930
Don't you have a bad feeling
about this?

792
01:22:35,440 --> 01:22:36,480
Excuse me.

793
01:22:37,310 --> 01:22:41,320
Do you have some strong cord
I could borrow?

794
01:22:44,740 --> 01:22:45,740
Cord?

795
01:22:49,700 --> 01:22:53,500
I need some, if you have any.

796
01:23:00,000 --> 01:23:04,470
I'll find some and bring it right up.

797
01:23:04,720 --> 01:23:05,720
Please.

798
01:23:22,860 --> 01:23:25,320
Maybe we should prepare ourselves
for the worst.

799
01:23:25,490 --> 01:23:26,490
Yes.

800
01:23:51,800 --> 01:23:54,640
This wet ground...

801
01:23:55,890 --> 01:23:57,980
...really gives you back ache.

802
01:23:58,600 --> 01:23:59,600
Well, Grandpa?

803
01:23:59,810 --> 01:24:00,810
What?

804
01:24:02,610 --> 01:24:06,240
Oh, that'll do, that's fine.

805
01:24:29,380 --> 01:24:30,380
What?

806
01:24:30,930 --> 01:24:32,600
I can hear something.

807
01:24:34,510 --> 01:24:36,110
A flute.

808
01:25:01,670 --> 01:25:02,880
The cord.

809
01:25:05,960 --> 01:25:06,960
Er...

810
01:25:08,170 --> 01:25:10,090
What's the hole for?

811
01:25:12,340 --> 01:25:15,300
It's for the garbage.

812
01:25:18,470 --> 01:25:20,470
Hard work.

813
01:25:23,060 --> 01:25:25,690
Thanks for everything.

814
01:25:44,210 --> 01:25:45,380
<i>What's this?</i>

815
01:26:28,210 --> 01:26:29,800
What are you burying him for?

816
01:27:46,540 --> 01:27:49,170
<i>Look on the bright side.</i>

817
01:27:50,080 --> 01:27:51,850
<i>OK!</i>

818
01:27:51,950 --> 01:27:56,090
<i>- Always be positive.</i>
<i>- OK!</i>

819
01:27:56,340 --> 01:28:00,050
<i>Oh, you can look away.</i>

820
01:28:00,290 --> 01:28:01,290
<i>Really?</i>

821
01:28:01,390 --> 01:28:03,930
<i>You can even stop.</i>

822
01:28:04,180 --> 01:28:05,270
<i>Go on, go on!</i>

823
01:28:05,520 --> 01:28:10,480
<i>But always get moving again.</i>

824
01:28:11,060 --> 01:28:16,990
<i>Even if no one is waiting for you.</i>

825
01:28:22,740 --> 01:28:24,580
<i>- Looking good.</i>
<i>- Let's go.</i>

826
01:28:24,990 --> 01:28:29,590
<i>Let's go slowly.</i>

827
01:28:30,000 --> 01:28:34,950
<i>With chins up high.</i>

828
01:28:35,050 --> 01:28:38,800
<i>Are we losers</i>

829
01:28:39,590 --> 01:28:42,930
<i>looking back to the past?</i>

830
01:28:43,930 --> 01:28:48,640
<i>Don't try too hard to forget.</i>

831
01:28:49,350 --> 01:28:56,950
<i>In the end, it's just a memory.</i>

832
01:29:03,530 --> 01:29:07,340
<i>Let's go together.</i>

833
01:29:07,460 --> 01:29:08,710
<i>Take me with you!</i>

834
01:29:08,880 --> 01:29:12,770
<i>Let's hold hands.</i>

835
01:29:13,460 --> 01:29:17,960
<i>Man is a weak...</i>

836
01:29:18,060 --> 01:29:22,340
<i>and lonely thing.</i>

837
01:29:22,440 --> 01:29:26,970
<i>So until we finally close our eyes,</i>

838
01:29:27,390 --> 01:29:34,790
<i>let's live to laugh and dance.</i>

839
01:30:34,120 --> 01:30:36,000
Where am I? Shit!

840
01:30:36,460 --> 01:30:37,710
What the hell!

841
01:30:38,460 --> 01:30:39,960
What is this! Damn.

842
01:31:12,740 --> 01:31:14,250
Good morning!

843
01:31:16,750 --> 01:31:18,080
Morning.

844
01:31:19,170 --> 01:31:20,790
Shit... Shit...

845
01:31:28,640 --> 01:31:29,640
What?

846
01:31:29,930 --> 01:31:30,930
What is it?

847
01:31:36,440 --> 01:31:37,440
Dad.

848
01:31:49,570 --> 01:31:51,530
- It can't be.
- They found out?

849
01:31:58,370 --> 01:32:00,830
What shall I do? What?

850
01:32:05,710 --> 01:32:07,090
Look! Look at this! Shit!

851
01:32:08,260 --> 01:32:09,260
Damn.

852
01:32:18,480 --> 01:32:20,440
Terue, look inside.

853
01:32:21,230 --> 01:32:22,270
Please.

854
01:32:22,690 --> 01:32:23,690
OK.

855
01:32:31,490 --> 01:32:32,490
Masao.

856
01:32:48,300 --> 01:32:51,900
<i>I shall go.</i>

857
01:32:52,510 --> 01:32:55,560
<i>Don't be stupid.</i>

858
01:32:57,180 --> 01:32:58,180
<i>I did it.</i>

859
01:32:58,350 --> 01:33:01,190
<i>I'm guilty of... everything.</i>

860
01:33:01,940 --> 01:33:04,310
<i>Too incredible!</i>

861
01:33:04,610 --> 01:33:07,360
<i>Nobody would believe it.</i>

862
01:33:07,730 --> 01:33:10,530
<i>Don't think about it.</i>

863
01:33:10,740 --> 01:33:13,620
<i>Masao, you did your best.</i>

864
01:33:13,820 --> 01:33:16,020
<i>Dad.</i>

865
01:33:16,700 --> 01:33:18,040
<i>I shall go.</i>

866
01:33:19,200 --> 01:33:22,330
<i>As long as you're here,</i>
<i>the Katakuri family will be OK.</i>

867
01:33:22,710 --> 01:33:24,710
<i>Don't worry.</i>

868
01:33:25,210 --> 01:33:31,010
<i>I gave up my life once during the war.</i>

869
01:33:31,880 --> 01:33:34,090
<i>Grandpa, wait,</i>

870
01:33:34,590 --> 01:33:37,500
<i>I'll go!</i>

871
01:33:37,600 --> 01:33:40,140
<i>Masayuki, good for you.</i>

872
01:33:40,480 --> 01:33:45,610
<i>Spoken like a real Japanese.</i>

873
01:33:46,230 --> 01:33:49,780
<i>But it's times like these,</i>
<i>when luck's run out,</i>

874
01:33:49,990 --> 01:33:55,160
<i>that old coots like me should go.</i>

875
01:33:55,820 --> 01:33:58,540
<i>No, it should be me.</i>

876
01:33:58,740 --> 01:34:00,830
<i>I suggested we bury them.</i>

877
01:34:01,040 --> 01:34:05,960
<i>Fact is, I dragged everyone here.</i>

878
01:34:06,960 --> 01:34:10,550
<i>I was wrong and I'm sorry.</i>

879
01:34:10,920 --> 01:34:12,970
<i>That's not true.</i>

880
01:34:13,180 --> 01:34:14,970
<i>That is true.</i>

881
01:34:15,510 --> 01:34:17,350
<i>No it's not.</i>

882
01:34:17,930 --> 01:34:21,330
<i>Yes it is.</i>

883
01:34:27,060 --> 01:34:28,980
<i>What is happiness?</i>

884
01:34:30,190 --> 01:34:33,400
<i>In all these years,</i>
<i>I've learnt just one thing.</i>

885
01:34:35,570 --> 01:34:39,990
<i>No one should die in a way</i>
<i>that saddens anyone.</i>

886
01:34:41,370 --> 01:34:46,460
<i>People should laugh at funerals:</i>
<i>'He did well to live this long'!</i>

887
01:34:50,460 --> 01:34:54,970
<i>How you die</i>
<i>is all down to how you live.</i>

888
01:34:56,550 --> 01:34:57,680
<i>Grandpa.</i>

889
01:34:58,050 --> 01:35:02,390
<i>Don't worry. God's kind to fools.</i>

890
01:35:08,940 --> 01:35:14,440
Shit! They followed me! Shit!
They're all following me!

891
01:35:29,920 --> 01:35:32,000
These are detectives
with the county police.

892
01:35:34,210 --> 01:35:35,380
Mr Katakuri,

893
01:35:37,510 --> 01:35:39,090
there's been a homicide.

894
01:35:50,480 --> 01:35:51,570
<i>Hello!</i>

895
01:35:54,780 --> 01:35:59,530
<i>Down at the foot of the mountain</i>
<i>a woman was killed at a guesthouse.</i>

896
01:35:59,740 --> 01:36:02,080
<i>We believe her lover did it,</i>

897
01:36:02,490 --> 01:36:05,540
<i>but we lost track of him.</i>

898
01:36:05,750 --> 01:36:09,040
Had any suspicious guests lately?

899
01:36:13,210 --> 01:36:14,880
This is Grandpa's.

900
01:36:24,310 --> 01:36:25,310
Dad.

901
01:36:25,680 --> 01:36:27,810
Could we see your guest register?

902
01:36:29,230 --> 01:36:31,650
And look in the grove out back?

903
01:36:31,860 --> 01:36:34,440
<i>- Asshole!</i>
<i>- Asshole?</i>

904
01:36:34,690 --> 01:36:37,990
You bastard! Damn you!

905
01:36:38,240 --> 01:36:41,660
<i>It's coming! Coming!</i>

906
01:36:42,240 --> 01:36:43,280
A hit!

907
01:36:44,660 --> 01:36:45,830
You bastard!

908
01:36:47,540 --> 01:36:48,540
Terue!

909
01:36:48,870 --> 01:36:50,000
Damn you all!

910
01:36:50,580 --> 01:36:51,830
- Let her go!
- Don't move.

911
01:36:54,130 --> 01:36:55,960
Shut up! Shoot, go on and shoot.

912
01:36:56,130 --> 01:36:58,420
Come on! Shoot, damn you.

913
01:36:58,800 --> 01:36:59,840
OK, OK, calm down.

914
01:37:01,640 --> 01:37:03,430
<i>- Darling!</i>
<i>- Let her go.</i>

915
01:37:04,010 --> 01:37:05,180
<i>- Let her go!</i>
<i>- Don't move.</i>

916
01:37:05,430 --> 01:37:06,470
Calm down.

917
01:37:07,220 --> 01:37:10,270
You killed the woman down
at the guesthouse!

918
01:37:10,520 --> 01:37:12,020
<i>You killed your wife!</i>

919
01:37:12,230 --> 01:37:14,110
Yes! Shut up, bastard!

920
01:37:14,560 --> 01:37:16,730
It's Nobuko's fault. It's her fault.

921
01:37:16,940 --> 01:37:18,110
Let go of her!

922
01:37:18,860 --> 01:37:19,860
Darling!

923
01:37:20,280 --> 01:37:21,780
Please stop.

924
01:37:26,080 --> 01:37:29,620
Why did you do it?

925
01:37:30,250 --> 01:37:32,460
Was it so unforgivable?

926
01:37:34,040 --> 01:37:37,130
Or was it unforgivable
because you loved her?

927
01:37:40,590 --> 01:37:42,220
- Shut up!
- Easy.

928
01:37:42,680 --> 01:37:44,220
I killed her because I loved her.

929
01:37:45,970 --> 01:37:47,890
What do you know, you bastard?

930
01:37:48,310 --> 01:37:50,020
How can you understand Nobuko and me'?

931
01:37:52,190 --> 01:37:53,480
Stand up!

932
01:37:54,150 --> 01:37:55,270
Nobuko!

933
01:37:56,230 --> 01:37:57,820
Nobuko, I'm sorry.

934
01:37:58,020 --> 01:37:59,230
Nobuko!

935
01:38:03,910 --> 01:38:04,910
Hey,

936
01:38:07,620 --> 01:38:12,960
did you love Nobuko that much?

937
01:38:14,290 --> 01:38:15,690
Me too.

938
01:38:16,750 --> 01:38:21,340
I love Terue more than
anything in the world.

939
01:38:24,680 --> 01:38:28,220
<i>I can understand your love.</i>

940
01:38:29,140 --> 01:38:31,980
<i>So you have to understand</i>
<i>how I feel too.</i>

941
01:38:32,890 --> 01:38:35,900
<i>So please let her go.</i>

942
01:38:36,440 --> 01:38:39,650
<i>I beg you.</i>

943
01:38:39,750 --> 01:38:44,150
The woman you're holding on to
so tightly now,

944
01:38:44,360 --> 01:38:46,490
isn't your wife.

945
01:38:46,700 --> 01:38:50,740
She's my beloved wife.

946
01:38:52,580 --> 01:38:54,460
Please understand.

947
01:38:54,870 --> 01:38:56,170
I beg you.

948
01:38:56,880 --> 01:38:57,880
Shut up!

949
01:38:59,090 --> 01:39:01,550
<i>OK, then take me hostage instead.</i>

950
01:39:01,760 --> 01:39:03,470
<i>Take me instead.</i>

951
01:39:03,670 --> 01:39:04,920
Shut up!

952
01:39:05,800 --> 01:39:07,090
<i>I beg you.</i>

953
01:39:08,010 --> 01:39:09,010
Never.

954
01:39:09,220 --> 01:39:10,260
I beg you.

955
01:39:17,400 --> 01:39:18,800
Please!

956
01:39:22,320 --> 01:39:23,610
<i>I beg you.</i>

957
01:39:25,320 --> 01:39:28,120
<i>Please.</i>

958
01:39:31,790 --> 01:39:33,200
I beg you.

959
01:39:36,080 --> 01:39:37,540
I beg you!

960
01:39:47,050 --> 01:39:48,180
Terue!

961
01:40:20,040 --> 01:40:21,210
Alright.

962
01:40:29,510 --> 01:40:30,510
Hey!

963
01:40:30,680 --> 01:40:31,800
Let go, you asshole!

964
01:40:33,760 --> 01:40:34,760
Masayuki!

965
01:40:40,400 --> 01:40:41,400
Nobuko!

966
01:40:42,610 --> 01:40:43,610
Masayuki!

967
01:40:54,660 --> 01:40:56,860
<i>Mum.</i>

968
01:40:57,660 --> 01:40:59,370
Be brave!

969
01:41:10,630 --> 01:41:17,360
<i>How precious... our son is!</i>

970
01:41:17,460 --> 01:41:18,470
<i>Masayuki.</i>

971
01:41:18,730 --> 01:41:20,930
<i>Mum.</i>

972
01:41:21,440 --> 01:41:22,560
<i>Are you all right?</i>

973
01:41:22,940 --> 01:41:24,730
<i>I'm all right.</i>

974
01:41:25,900 --> 01:41:27,860
<i>I'm right here.</i>

975
01:41:28,190 --> 01:41:30,060
<i>Dad.</i>

976
01:41:30,160 --> 01:41:31,240
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

977
01:41:32,280 --> 01:41:35,530
<i>I wasn't a good son.</i>

978
01:41:35,910 --> 01:41:37,370
<i>Nonsense.</i>

979
01:41:38,410 --> 01:41:42,290
<i>But I'm proud to be your son.</i>

980
01:41:43,790 --> 01:41:46,090
<i>It hurts! It hurts!</i>

981
01:41:46,420 --> 01:41:47,800
<i>Be brave.</i>

982
01:41:49,130 --> 01:41:51,330
<i>Sis.</i>

983
01:41:51,670 --> 01:41:53,930
<i>You're quite a babe.</i>

984
01:41:58,310 --> 01:42:02,910
<i>So, keep trying.</i>

985
01:42:04,690 --> 01:42:08,090
<i>Don't die!</i>

986
01:42:10,780 --> 01:42:12,580
Masayuki!

987
01:42:23,290 --> 01:42:24,290
Is that it?

988
01:42:30,380 --> 01:42:32,970
- It's this big.
- This big?

989
01:42:33,170 --> 01:42:35,260
- A graze?
- This big?

990
01:42:35,800 --> 01:42:37,680
Just a scratch!

991
01:43:02,500 --> 01:43:04,160
That's good.

992
01:43:18,050 --> 01:43:19,720
Hey, wait!

993
01:43:43,040 --> 01:43:44,830
<i>Where's Pochi?</i>

994
01:43:45,040 --> 01:43:46,370
Find Pochi!

995
01:43:50,130 --> 01:43:51,170
<i>Pochi!</i>

996
01:43:52,340 --> 01:43:53,500
<i>Pochi!</i>

997
01:43:54,050 --> 01:43:56,650
<i>Pochi!</i>

998
01:43:57,380 --> 01:44:00,430
- Where are you going?
- Darling!

999
01:44:00,640 --> 01:44:02,810
- Impossible!
- Darling!

1000
01:44:03,060 --> 01:44:04,060
Masao!

1001
01:44:05,560 --> 01:44:06,560
<i>Pochi.</i>

1002
01:44:06,980 --> 01:44:08,020
Give me your paw.

1003
01:44:08,230 --> 01:44:10,770
Give Dad your paw.

1004
01:44:11,020 --> 01:44:12,020
<i>Incredible.</i>

1005
01:44:17,280 --> 01:44:18,610
<i>You OK?</i>

1006
01:44:19,280 --> 01:44:21,120
<i>- Darling!</i>
<i>- Pochi.</i>

1007
01:44:21,570 --> 01:44:23,410
<i>Pochi, that was dose.</i>

1008
01:44:23,620 --> 01:44:27,210
- Right, that's it, it's OK.
- Sorry.

1009
01:44:28,120 --> 01:44:29,710
<i>Here it comes.</i>

1010
01:44:30,290 --> 01:44:31,960
Everyone, stick together!

1011
01:44:32,130 --> 01:44:33,170
Right.

1012
01:44:35,340 --> 01:44:36,760
<i>Hold hands.</i>

1013
01:44:36,960 --> 01:44:39,160
<i>Yes.</i>

1014
01:44:39,760 --> 01:44:41,890
<i>Hold my hand tight, Yurie.</i>

1015
01:44:42,100 --> 01:44:44,060
<i>- Mum, Pochi!</i>
<i>- Grandpa!</i>

1016
01:44:44,260 --> 01:44:45,770
<i>Everyone!</i>

1017
01:44:46,470 --> 01:44:47,980
<i>Hold hands!</i>

1018
01:44:52,190 --> 01:44:53,610
Go for it, everyone!

1019
01:45:04,080 --> 01:45:06,120
<i>Grandpa's gone.</i>

1020
01:45:06,330 --> 01:45:07,370
<i>There's Grandpa!</i>

1021
01:45:24,140 --> 01:45:26,430
<i>Grandpa laughed and said,</i>

1022
01:45:26,970 --> 01:45:30,770
<i>"Never give up saying 'that's life'.</i>

1023
01:45:32,400 --> 01:45:33,440
<i>Remember,</i>

1024
01:45:33,940 --> 01:45:39,650
<i>anything can happen in life".</i>

1025
01:45:40,990 --> 01:45:45,990
<i>The human race has survived</i>
<i>thousands and millions of years,</i>

1026
01:45:46,450 --> 01:45:48,490
<i>living bravely and tenaciously.</i>

1027
01:45:53,790 --> 01:45:55,390
Darling.

1028
01:46:06,050 --> 01:46:07,810
<i>He's awake.</i>

1029
01:46:08,010 --> 01:46:09,470
<i>Hey, hey.</i>

1030
01:46:11,480 --> 01:46:12,770
Can you see us?

1031
01:46:12,980 --> 01:46:14,310
You OK?

1032
01:46:15,690 --> 01:46:16,940
Survived.

1033
01:46:20,480 --> 01:46:21,570
Thank God.

1034
01:46:27,870 --> 01:46:30,470
<i>Pochi.</i>

1035
01:46:54,060 --> 01:46:55,060
Wait.

1036
01:46:55,980 --> 01:46:57,560
Look over here.

1037
01:47:19,590 --> 01:47:21,130
It's beautiful.

1038
01:47:30,970 --> 01:47:34,600
<i>So, let's go! Let's go!</i>

1039
01:47:34,810 --> 01:47:38,440
<i>The sun is watching with a smile.</i>

1040
01:47:38,650 --> 01:47:42,110
<i>Let's sing!</i>

1041
01:47:42,210 --> 01:47:45,700
<i>Like the birds, aim for the sky.</i>

1042
01:47:45,900 --> 01:47:49,550
<i>Let's laugh!</i>

1043
01:47:49,650 --> 01:47:53,580
<i>Leave your sadness to the wind.</i>

